                  <date type="foundation" notBefore="1200" notAfter="1500"/>
                  
                  <ab type="history">Local tradition claims the foundation of the church in the <date notBefore="1200" notAfter="1300">time of King <persName ref="PRS4327GabraMa">Gabra Masqal</persName>
                     </date>. 
                     The church must have been founded in the <date notAfter="1500">pre-15th century period</date>, and be re-established during the reign of King Yoḥannǝs IV (1872-1889). 
                     The church of <placeName ref="INS0082UMQ">ʿUra Masqal</placeName> (now deserted), on the top of the rock, appears to be an older institution.
                  </ab>
